sql:
SELECT game_id, score
FROM games_teams
WHERE score > 80;

external_knowledge:
Top-ranked teams refer to those that finished within the top 5 in the regular season standings; 
Team performance is tracked across multiple seasons, with cumulative statistics providing insights into long-term trends and player composition;
The team's average height and weight can influence performance in various sports, with taller and heavier teams possibly having advantages in certain sports;
Primary and secondary positions indicate the versatility and depth of a team's lineup.
